{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4f09420e39","title":"对袁血卒来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d2f3c298df","index":0,"year":1975,"month":12,"day":18,"articleId":"4f09420e39"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"5e94441bd4","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4f09420e39","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"袁血卒1975年12月13日给毛泽东写信说，我1927年入党，1931年初受中央军委委派到二十六路军搞兵运，组织了宁都暴动，成立红五军团。从中央苏区突围后，在上海曾两次被捕。1937年到延安，经4年审查，恢复了党籍。1958年转业到天津化工学院工作。文化大革命中又经过反复调查，再次证明我在两次被捕中没有暴露党员和红军指挥员身份，是执行了而不是违背了党的隐蔽政策。1974年恢复党的组织生活，但至今没有工作。我在军队工作几十年，热爱军队，请求批准我回部队工作。毛泽东的批语，写在中共中央办公厅1975年12月17日印的这封来信摘要上。1978年，袁血卒被任命为民政部副部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"540a0a084b","type":"title","text":"对袁血卒来信的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4f09420e39"},{"id":"5e94441bd4","type":"paragraph","text":"送大津市党委的处。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4f09420e39"},{"id":"2224f2f9a2","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4f09420e39"},{"id":"7374ef1ebd","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4f09420e39"}],"page":{"id":"f6f2d6c899","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"4f09420e39","start":126,"end":126}}}},"__N_SSG":true}